WIDGET_HELP_TEXT_WM-TILE: Use a Tile to group together a set of widgets.
WIDGET_HELP_TEXT_WM-BREADCRUMB: Use a breadcrumb for navigation. You can bind dataset with variable having structure as [{'label': 'Home','icon': 'glyphicon glyphicon-home','link': '#/Home'}]

WIDGET_HELP_TEXT_WM-TEXTAREA: Enables a user to enter in multiple lines of text.
WIDGET_HELP_TEXT_WM-SELECT: The Select Menu widget provides a way for users to select an item from a drop-down list of choices.
WIDGET_HELP_TEXT_WM-RADIO: Radio buttons let a user select only one of a limited number of choices.

WIDGET_HELP_TEXT_WM-SWITCH: Switch displays checked/unchecked states as a button.
WIDGET_HELP_TEXT_WM-CHECKBOX: Checkboxes let a user select zero or more options of a limited number of choices.

WIDGET_HELP_TEXT_WM-COLORPICKER: Color Picker widget that allows user to choose any sort of color.

WIDGET_HELP_TEXT_WM-IFRAME: Embeds an HTML document in a frame on the current page.

 If you want the slider to return discrete integer values, set the discreteValues property to the number of discrete values between the minimum slider position and the maximum slider position.
